      "originalText": "now how can i serve all this dist file(html css js)\n\n1) NGINIX or use lib like SERVE\n\n\nhere i am going with SERVE:\n1) use : npm install -g serve\n2) then run : serve\n\nnote: make sure the root is dist:",
