      "text": "but here: i always have to add this port like 3000\nwhen ever i want to visit to my site which is so ugly\ntbh. so u have to make an super user:\n\n1) sudo apt update\n2)sudo  apt install nodejs\n3) sudo node\n4) sudo npm install\n5) sudo npm install -g serve\n6) sudo serve -p 80\n",
      "fontSize": 19.640748819622985,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "but here: i always have to add this port like 3000 when ever i want to visit to my site which is so ugly tbh. so u have to make an super user:\n\n1) sudo apt update\n2)sudo  apt install nodejs\n3) sudo node\n4) sudo npm install\n5) sudo npm install -g serve\n6) sudo serve -p 80\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
