      "updated": 1775677406871,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "so here the thing is called POP : point of present, all over the world ,\nand let say trying to find an file on EC2. so the CDN lets u to\nreachs the closest one. and the file gets caches close to u.\n\nbut u have to provide the source URL to CDN \n\nalso u  have to store ur content file some where:\nso here the Object stores comes:\n",
      "fontSize": 34.9527254971591,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "so here the thing is called POP : point of present, all over the world , and let say trying to find an file on EC2. so the CDN lets u to reachs the closest one. and the file gets caches close to u.\n\nbut u have to provide the source URL to CDN \n\nalso u  have to store ur content file some where:\nso here the Object stores comes:\n",
